:"所以咪叫你搵過份快d 走<br />\n做得一兩星期個d 好心你就咪撚寫啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a265460ef0e0f2b9d116e177a88a0cc16072344","tid":528942,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"同埋nursing 真係唔難搵工<br />\n係睇你做唔做嘅姐"}]}